{"word":"G127 - αἰδώς - aidṓs - ahee-doce' - Reverence","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αἰδώς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>aidṓs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ahee-doce'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Reverence"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நாணம், பக்தி - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a sense of shame, modesty"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Perhaps from <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G1492 - εἴδω - eídō - i'-do/1492\">G1492</a> (through the idea of <i>downcast</i> eyes); <i>bashfulness</i>, that is, (towards men), <i>modesty</i> or (towards God) <i>awe:</i> - reverence, shamefacedness."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}